name: They're-VVolves by M8N
description:
I introduce to you "VVolves", the other side of me that emerges because "infinity M8N" forges souls from time to time. From the age that I still believe in hopes and dreams, the 7-year life cycle, to the age of dealing "if I still have sleep and food for today.. that's enough", until "karma is the key".

And in between those times, I realized that it was "VVolves" that often kept me going, made me laugh, and even my steps were colored because of them. Although I know it's very ironic because these "VVolves" are from a life I regretted earlier.
